        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–5. 1: Oxybelus lusitanicus female habitus. 2: Metanotum showing broad yellow band and bifid lamella (arrowed). 3: Lateral view of male clypeal keel showing secondary tooth (arrowed). 4: Female nectaring on Helichrysum italicum. 5: Male nectaring on Polygonum equisetiforme." ;
